{
  "stem": "24212.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had false papers for most countries, just in case.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah, well that was one part of the resistance, evidently, that manufacturered false papers, false ID cards, false passport, forged birth certificates, especially for Jews-- and what else-- ration cards, by the ton I'm sure, if you added it all together, because there were so many people in hiding.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Don't forget it wasn't just the Jews who were running from persecution.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But there were lots of people who were either part of the resistance or not part of the resistance, but suspected as part of the resistance.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they were persecuted too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So many of them went abroad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And many of them went into hiding, or lived under false-- with false identities.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The only name I really remember is Michalska, because I always liked that name.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know for what reason.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the others must have sort of come and gone, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah, that I remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, we-- we had some strange encounters, and we had some difficulties.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For instance, people fleeing for their lives grab all kinds of strange things to lug with them, OK?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one thing I remember is a couple who had silver candelabra.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very beautiful, I must say, if I remember correctly, and must have been very valuable, but very heavy.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went on the mountains-- you know, uphill, downhill, uphill.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they just go, oh, I cannot carry it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Would you help me?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so then we decided that before we go, we will look what people have, and if it's silver candelabra, no way.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One couple carried a teddy bear, which I still remember.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just a little teddy bear that doesn't weigh so much.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
